==Korean==
===Noun===
'''구름''' (''gureum'')
# [[cloud]] cf. Greek (''gloutos'') "[[buttock]]"

====Synonyms====
*[[운]] ([[雲]], ''un'') 

====Derived terms====
*구름 [[다리]] (''-dari'') elevated [[bridge]]
*구름 [[바다]] (''-bada'') [[sea]] of clouds
; Predicatives 
*구름 [[개다]] (''-gaeda'') To be [[clear]]ed (of clouds)
*구름 [[끼다]] (''-kkida'') To be [[cloud]]ed
*구름 [[덮히다]] (''-deophida'') To be [[cover]]ed with clouds
*구름 [[잡다]] (''-jabda, -japda'') To be as [[fantastic]] as "to catch the cloud"

